### QuickBite Menu Service - API Testing
### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8081
@contentType = application/json

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/actuator/health

### 1. Get Available Menu (Client endpoint)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/menu
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

### 2. Get Menu Item by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/menu/1
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

### 3. Create New Menu Item
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/menu
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "Hamburguesa Clásica",
  "description": "Deliciosa hamburguesa con carne, lechuga, tomate y queso",
  "price": 8990.0,
  "category": "Hamburguesas"
}

### 4. Get All Menu Items (Admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/menu/all
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

### 5. Update Menu Item Price
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/menu/1/price
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "newPrice": 9990.0
}

### 6. Update Menu Item Availability
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/menu/1/availability
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "available": false
}

### 7. Update Complete Menu Item
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/menu/1
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "Hamburguesa Premium",
  "description": "Hamburguesa con ingredientes premium",
  "price": 12990.0,
  "category": "Hamburguesas Premium",
  "available": true
}

### 8. Get Menu Items by Category
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/menu/category/Hamburguesas
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

### 9. Get Unavailable Items
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/menu/unavailable
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

### 10. Delete Menu Item
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/menu/1
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

### 11. Get Application Info
GET {{baseUrl}}/actuator/info
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

### 12. Get Metrics
GET {{baseUrl}}/actuator/metrics
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
